好的,各位,我们有个问题
OK, people. We've got a problem.

173
00:13:47,860 --> 00:13:50,897
其中一颗钻石就藏在这儿的旋转木马
One of the diamonds is hidden here,on the Roundabout.

174
00:13:51,020 --> 00:13:52,897
我必须留在后面来守护它
I must stay behind to guard it.

175
00:13:53,020 --> 00:13:55,659
要找出其它两颗你们会需要这份地图
To find the other two,you will need this map.

176
00:13:56,540 --> 00:13:58,417
你们必须前往北边山上
You must head north into the mountains.

177
00:13:58,540 --> 00:14:00,337
没时间好磨蹭了
There is no time to waste.

178
00:14:01,580 --> 00:14:05,175
希望你有提供我们适合的交通工具
Well, I hope you've supplied us with an appropriate mode of transportation.

179
00:14:10,580 --> 00:14:12,855
哈哈,我倒车一下
Whoops! Ha, ha, I'll just back up.

180
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:15,050
勉强算是东方快车,亲爱的!
It's hardly the Orient Express, darling!

181
00:14:15,180 --> 00:14:16,659
它有头等舱吗?
Does it have first class?

182
00:14:16,780 --> 00:14:17,929
什么?
What?

183
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:20,733
谨慎保管这个小小魔法盒
Take good care of this little box of tricks.

184
00:14:20,860 --> 00:14:23,249
紧要关头时可能会救你们一命
It may save you in your hour of need.

185
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:25,940
佛罗伦丝,撑下去,我会回来的
Florence, hold on. I'll be back.

186
00:14:26,820 --> 00:14:28,731
-我保证
-别太久唷
- I promise.- Don't be too long.

187
00:14:29,780 --> 00:14:32,135
不管发生什么事
千万别怪你自己
Whatever happens,you mustn't blame yourself.

188
00:14:32,260 --> 00:14:34,171
不,交给我们吧
- No, leave that to us.- Hm!

189
00:14:34,300 --> 00:14:35,369
所有人登车!
All aboard!

190
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:38,617
孩子们别担心我们的朋友会救我们的
Don't worry, children.Our friends will save us.

191
00:14:38,740 --> 00:14:42,619
蒸汽正常,锅炉室正常活塞正常!
Steam, check. Furnace, check.Pistons, check. Wahey!

192
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:46,855
乘客抱歉,忘了还有乘客
Sorry. Passengers.I forgot the passengers.

193
00:14:50,260 --> 00:14:51,693
树木好!
Hello, trees!

194
00:14:51,820 --> 00:14:53,572
小鸟好!
Hello, birds!

195
00:14:53,700 --> 00:14:55,497
恐怖凛冽的雾气好
Hello, scary freezing mist.

196
00:14:56,340 --> 00:14:57,978
幸亏它们没听到
Oh, dear. Lucky they can't hear me.

197
00:14:58,100 --> 00:15:00,330
我不希望它们认为
我是辆恐怖列车
I wouldn't want them thinking I'm a scaredy-train.

198
00:15:03,300 --> 00:15:04,938
哦,佛罗伦丝
Oh, Florence.

199
00:15:14,540 --> 00:15:17,418
不知我们去何方,不知他们知不知道
I wonder where we're going.I wonder if they even know.

200
00:15:17,540 --> 00:15:20,930
不知道他们知不知道我根本不知道,哦,这太刺激了!
I wonder if they know that I don't even know. Oh, this is exciting!

201
00:15:21,060 --> 00:15:22,857
-嘟狗-干嘛?
- Dougal.- Yeah?

202
00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:25,574
千万不要觉得内疚,只因为这全是你的错
You mustn't feel guilty just because it's all your fault.

203
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:28,658
-我?-不好意思,那样说不太好
- Me?- Oh, sorry, that didn't come out right.

204
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:30,372
我的错?
My fault?

205
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:31,933
我做了什么?
What did I do?

206
00:15:32,060 --> 00:15:34,290
除了毁掉旋转木马...
What, apart from wrecking the Roundabout,

207
00:15:34,420 --> 00:15:36,138
困住佛罗伦丝和孩子们...
trapping Florence and the children

208
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:39,491
还导致一个企图冰冻太阳的疯子脱逃
and causing the escape of a maniac intent on freezing the sun?

209
00:15:39,620 --> 00:15:42,180
我只是想牙缝塞点糖果
I only wanted to get my teeth into some sweeties.

210
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:46,452
对,就是糖果起的因也许是冰面包
Yeah, it starts with some sweets, man,maybe an iced bun,

211
00:15:46,580 --> 00:15:49,617
在你察觉之前你就已经一天吃了两包
and before you know it,you're on two bags a day.

212
00:15:49,740 --> 00:15:51,571
我晓得,我有过经验
I know man, I've been there.

213
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:54,498
也许你有个问题我的毛茸茸朋友?
Maybe you've got, like, a problem,my furry friend?

214
00:15:54,620 --> 00:15:58,090
我没有! 我不会放弃的直到我尽我一切力量...
I have not! And I'll not rest until I've done everything in my power

215
00:15:58,300 --> 00:16:00,131
把事情烤好
to bake things right.

216
00:16:00,260 --> 00:16:02,091
我是指把事情搞好
I mean make things right.

217
00:16:02,220 --> 00:16:04,415
老天,越来越冷了
Goodness, it's getting cold.

218
00:16:04,540 --> 00:16:08,055
告诉我一下在这里我螺栓螺帽都要冻僵了!
Tell me about it.I'm freezing my nuts and bolts off here!

219
00:16:26,860 --> 00:16:29,613
我必须说,你们全做的很棒
I must say,you're all doing a wonderful job.

220
00:16:29,740 --> 00:16:31,810
继续保持下去
Keep up the good work.

221
00:16:31,940 --> 00:16:34,090
晚餐吃什么? 我饿扁了!
What's for dinner anyway?I'm famished!

222
00:16:36,260 --> 00:16:40,299
我懂了,沉默以待,是不是?
哼!
Oh, I see, the silent treatment is it?Huh!

223
00:16:42,540 --> 00:16:45,498
幸好我带了些秘密补给!
It's lucky I brought some secret supplies. Mm!

224
00:16:45,620 --> 00:16:47,497
满月
Ah, full moon.

225
00:16:48,460 --> 00:16:51,577
听说满月教人陷入罗曼蒂克气氛中
They say the full moon puts people in the mood for romance.

226
00:16:53,180 --> 00:16:57,492
多么完美的场地呀,刚适合办户外韦瓦第节庆演唱
What a perfect venue for an open-air Verdi festival.

227
00:16:57,620 --> 00:16:59,417
这里会挤的人山人海的
People would flock here.

228
00:17:01,420 --> 00:17:04,492
就连羊也受不了那种噪音
Not even sheep
would flock to that noise.

229
00:17:10,660 --> 00:17:12,571
惨了
- Uh-oh.- Mm?

230
00:17:13,460 --> 00:17:15,098
真是九死一生
That was a close shave.

231
00:17:16,100 --> 00:17:18,455
我的口香糖! 哦,不!
My gobstoppers! Oh, no!

232
00:17:18,580 --> 00:17:20,172
只剩一个了!
There's only one left!

233
00:17:20,300 --> 00:17:22,768
对! 我们都该好好睡个美容觉了
Right! It's time we all got some beauty sleep.

234
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:23,969
狄伦?
Dylan?

235
00:17:24,940 --> 00:17:26,089
狄伦!
Dylan!

236
00:17:26,220 --> 00:17:28,688
-怎...怎么?-睡觉时间到了!
- Wha... What?- Bedtime!

237
00:17:28,820 --> 00:17:31,459
老天,谢谢你叫醒我让我晓得
Gee, thanks for waking me up to let me know.

238
00:17:31,580 --> 00:17:32,808
应该要有人来守卫
Someone should keep watch.

239
00:17:32,940 --> 00:17:34,737
-我在想...-真是太感谢你了
- I was thinking...- Good of you to offer.

240
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:36,179
-什么?-晚安
- What?- Good night.

241
00:17:36,300 --> 00:17:39,133
-晚安,各位亲爱的-晚安安,爱蜜楚
- Good night, darlings.- Night-night, Ermindude.

242
00:17:39,260 --> 00:17:40,579
什么?
Eh? What?

243
00:17:40,700 --> 00:17:42,372
现在我是沉睡的列车了
Now my impression of a sleeper train.

244
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:44,411
等等,等等...
Wait, wait...

245
00:17:45,340 --> 00:17:48,059
糟糕,我牙膏用完了!
Oh, no. I've run out of toothpaste!

246
00:18:07,220 --> 00:18:09,017
我干嘛非得当守卫犬?
Why do I have to be the guard dog?

247
00:18:09,140 --> 00:18:12,974
不能是守卫蜗牛或守卫母牛或...?
What's wrong with a guard snail or a guard cow or...?

248
00:18:13,100 --> 00:18:14,852
谁在那里?
Who goes there?

249
00:18:14,980 --> 00:18:17,540
是敌是友? 还是...
Friend or foe? Or...

250
00:18:17,660 --> 00:18:20,538
糜鹿? 感觉有点忧郁(蓝色)?
...moose? F-Feeling a bit blue?

251
00:18:20,660 --> 00:18:22,537
你不是唯一这样的
You're not the only one.

252
00:18:24,740 --> 00:18:27,208
是你朋友吗?
Oh, is this a friend of yours?

253
00:18:29,300 --> 00:18:31,177
我想这代表不是吧!
I'll take that as a no!

254
00:18:33,220 --> 00:18:35,893
-嘟狗?-嘟嘟狗?
- Dougal?- Dougie?

255
00:18:36,020 --> 00:18:38,136
-嘟狗?-嘟狗?
- Dougal?- Dougal?

256
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:41,411
-嘟狗?-小嘟? 小嘟?
- Dougal?- Doogie? Doogie, man?

257
00:18:41,540 --> 00:18:43,178
出来,嘟狗! 出来,嘟狗!
Here, Dougal. Here, Dougal.

258
00:18:44,140 --> 00:18:47,530
我发现个痕迹.也许会指引我们找到他
Oooh, I've found a trail.Maybe it'll lead us to him.

259
00:18:47,660 --> 00:18:50,128
或者也许会指引我们找到...
Or maybe it'll lead us to that...

260
00:18:51,140 --> 00:18:53,051
糜鹿
...moose.

261
00:18:54,620 --> 00:18:57,054
我觉得他想告诉我们什么事
I think he's trying to tell us something.

262
00:18:57,180 --> 00:18:59,216
你有见过我们朋友嘟狗吗?
Have you seen our friend Dougal?

263
00:18:59,340 --> 00:19:03,652
又大又黑的鼻子,脚上的毛一团乱糟糟的
Big black nose,looks like a bad hair day on legs?

264
00:19:03,780 --> 00:19:05,532
你在浪费时间,布莱恩
You're wasting your time, Brian.

265
00:19:05,660 --> 00:19:07,855
谁听过会讲话的糜鹿呢?
Whoever heard of a talking moose?

266
00:19:07,980 --> 00:19:10,540
该说是唱歌剧的母牛吧
Says the opera-singing cow.

267
00:19:12,980 --> 00:19:15,130
听着,我觉得他想要我们跟他走
Look, I think he wants us to follow him.

268
00:19:18,220 --> 00:19:20,017
快点! 用最快速度前进吧!
Come on! As fast as you can!

269
00:19:37,060 --> 00:19:41,815
现在,你这低等智慧的毛刷
通通老实招来
Now, you dim-witted draft excluder,tell me everything.

270
00:19:41,940 --> 00:19:44,170
我是只非常快乐的小狗
Well, I was a very happy puppy.

271
00:19:44,300 --> 00:19:47,417
我最初的印象便是和佛罗伦丝接网球
My first memories are of catching tennis balls with Florence.

272
00:19:47,540 --> 00:19:50,896
-后来我长大了,她...-不,你这进化迟钝的怪胎!
- Then, as I grew up, she...- No, you follicly-enhanced freak!

273
00:19:51,020 --> 00:19:53,409
告诉我钻石的事
Tell me about the diamonds,

274
00:19:53,540 --> 00:19:56,498
否则我教你求生不得求死不能!
or I'll make you wish you'd packed a pooper-scooper!

275
00:19:56,620 --> 00:19:59,453
我? 我什么都不知道甚至连地图都没有
Me? I don't know anything.I don't even have the map.

276
00:19:59,580 --> 00:20:03,129
原来有地图啊
So, there's a map, eh?

277
00:20:04,540 --> 00:20:06,212
不不不不...没有地图
No, no, no, no... No map.

278
00:20:06,340 --> 00:20:08,774
他们当然不会放心交给你携带
Well, of course they wouldn't trust you with it.

279
00:20:08,900 --> 00:20:10,970
你只是只小笨狗
You're just a silly little dog.

280
00:20:11,100 --> 00:20:13,455
你可能会埋起来或嚼了它!
You'd probably bury it or chew it!

281
00:20:14,540 --> 00:20:16,496
地图在谁身上?
So, who does have the map?

282
00:20:17,380 --> 00:20:19,291
我绝不会说的!
- Eh?- I'll never tell!

283
00:20:19,420 --> 00:20:20,489
不会吗?
Oh, no?

284
00:20:20,620 --> 00:20:24,135
山姆,别再拿着那根掸子刷来刷去的了
Sam, stop mincing around with that duster.

285
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:28,048
给他严刑逼供直到他全盘托出为止
Torture this boarding house for fleas until he tells us everything.

286
00:20:28,180 --> 00:20:29,169
是,长官!
Yes, sir!

287
00:20:30,300 --> 00:20:32,131
那好吧,酷刑!
Right, then. Torture!

288
00:20:32,260 --> 00:20:34,615
听着,这种事我还不大熟
所以...
Look, this is all a bit new to me,so, erm...

289
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:36,492
你最怕的是什么?
what is it you're most afraid of?

290
00:20:40,940 --> 00:20:44,171
不久就可以恢复我全部的实力了
It won't be long now until I have my full powers back.

291
00:20:44,300 --> 00:20:45,653
然后我...
Then I...

292
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:48,214
不! 不,不! 不要那样!
Oh, no! No, no! Not that!

293
00:20:48,340 --> 00:20:49,898
很好,山姆!
Good Sam!

294
00:20:50,020 --> 00:20:51,419
好好玩吧!
Enjoy yourself!

295
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:53,451
拜不要! 别再来了!
No, please! Ooh, no more!

296
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:56,811
-26...
-哦,我受不了了!
- 26...- Ooh, I can't stand it!

297
00:20:56,940 --> 00:21:00,615
27...他不可能吃下更多了!
27... He can't possibly take much more of this!

298
00:21:00,740 --> 00:21:02,617
你已吃了27个方糖!
You've eaten 27 sugar cubes!

299
00:21:02,740 --> 00:21:07,052
你得逼我吃下一百个
我才会告诉你一切!
You'll have to make me eat 100 before I tell you anything!

300
00:21:07,700 --> 00:21:09,531
不,不! 拜!
No, no! Please!

301
00:21:09,660 --> 00:21:11,730
钻石很快就会是我的了
Soon the diamonds will be mine

302
00:21:11,900 --> 00:21:16,018
而我就能把这丑陋的绿色星球...
and I'll be able to turn this hideous green planet

303
00:21:16,140 --> 00:21:19,212
变成一处可爱的冰冻荒地
into a lovely frozen wasteland.

304
00:21:19,340 --> 00:21:21,649
太可怕了!
This is terrible!

305
00:21:26,580 --> 00:21:29,299
-不,你千万不可!
-再来一点
- No, you mustn't!- Little more.

306
00:21:29,420 --> 00:21:32,139
-...你不动手了吗?
-还要多久? 我在工作...
-...don't you?- How long will this take? I'm working...

307
00:21:33,340 --> 00:21:37,015
喔! 你在害死我!
- Eh?- Ooh, Ow! You're killing me!

308
00:21:44,100 --> 00:21:46,933
听起来蛮痛的!
- Argh!- Ooh, that sounded painful!

309
00:21:47,060 --> 00:21:50,370
嘻嘻! 干的漂亮,山姆
Hee, hee! Excellent work, Sam.

310
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:54,413
不! 少碰我,你这邪恶的恶魔!
No! Leave me alone, you evil fiend!

311
00:21:54,540 --> 00:21:56,531
你在碎碎个什么劲?
What are you talking about?

312
00:21:56,660 --> 00:21:58,890
是我啊...爱蜜楚
It's me - Ermintrude.

313
00:21:59,020 --> 00:22:02,456
你能五分钟后再来吗?
我才刚开始玩的开心呢
Could you come back in five minutes?I was just starting to enjoy myself.

314
00:22:02,580 --> 00:22:04,013
快点,嘟狗
Oh, come on, Dougal.

315
00:22:07,980 --> 00:22:09,732
蒸汽全开向后!
Full steam backwards!

316
00:22:12,900 --> 00:22:14,618
解决掉他,山姆
Finish him off, Sam.

317
00:22:14,740 --> 00:22:16,696
我们该...
It's time we...

318
00:22:18,300 --> 00:22:21,053
狗!
你对他做了什么好事,你这白痴?
The dog! What have you done with him, you idiot?

319
00:22:21,180 --> 00:22:26,015
长官,我被一头飞天母牛给压扁了!
Ooh... Well, sir, I got flattened by a flying cow. Oooh!

320
00:22:27,540 --> 00:22:29,019
别跑的这么快!
Not so fast!

321
00:22:29,140 --> 00:22:32,530
放开我的尾巴,畜生
Ow! Ooh, let go of my tail,you br-brute.

322
00:22:32,660 --> 00:22:33,649
爱蜜楚!
Ermintrude!

323
00:22:33,780 --> 00:22:35,532
再快一点!
Faster!

324
00:22:40,980 --> 00:22:42,208
倒车,倒车!
Back it up, back it up!

325
00:22:43,460 --> 00:22:46,418
你真好心来拜访我
How nice of you to drop in.

326
00:22:46,540 --> 00:22:47,939
拉!
Pull!

327
00:22:48,860 --> 00:22:51,499
很抱歉,无法久留了
Sorry, can't stay long.

328
00:22:54,820 --> 00:22:56,333
极速飞车!
- Aaaagh!- Uh-oh! Whiplash!

329
00:22:56,540 --> 00:22:57,814
你好
Hello.

330
00:22:57,940 --> 00:23:00,738
她从这个角度看比较好看
Ah, she looks a lot better from this angle.

331
00:23:00,860 --> 00:23:05,217
等她成为座上佳肴时会更好看
She'll look a lot better when she's being served with a side order of fries.

332
00:23:06,220 --> 00:23:07,573
去追他们!
After them!

333
00:23:11,740 --> 00:23:14,698
这里又冷又不舒服
我们在哪里?
This is cold and very unpleasant. Where are we?

334
00:23:14,820 --> 00:23:17,459
-继续走! 继续走!
-一定有别条路的
- Keep going! Keep going!- There must be another way.

335
00:23:17,660 --> 00:23:19,616
对,对
Yeah, man. Yeah, yeah.

336
00:23:19,740 --> 00:23:21,537
继续走,各位
Keep going, people.

337
00:23:23,940 --> 00:23:26,773
我是火车,不是雪橇!
I'm a train, not a snowboard!

338
00:23:26,900 --> 00:23:28,015
"吧-吧-吧碰"
Ba-ba-ba bom

339
00:23:28,220 --> 00:23:29,778
"继续转呀转"
Keep spinnin', spinnin' around

340
00:23:29,900 --> 00:23:31,219
"吧-吧-吧碰"
Ba-ba-ba bom

341
00:23:31,340 --> 00:23:32,898
"继续转呀转"
Keep spinnin', spinnin' around

342
00:23:33,020 --> 00:23:34,009
"吧-吧-吧碰"
Ba-ba-ba bom

343
00:23:34,180 --> 00:23:35,215
"继续转呀转"
Keep spinnin', spinnin' around

344
00:23:35,340 --> 00:23:36,329
"吧-吧-吧碰"
Ba-ba-ba bom

345
00:23:36,460 --> 00:23:38,735
"继续转呀转"
Keep spinnin', spinnin' around

346
00:23:38,860 --> 00:23:40,976
"啊"
A-a-a-ah

347
00:23:41,100 --> 00:23:42,169
"吧-吧-吧碰"
Ba-ba-ba bom

348
00:23:45,140 --> 00:23:48,894
我的用途是行驶...不是滑雪!
I was made to shunt...not to ski!

349
00:23:51,820 --> 00:23:55,495
哇,好深
Whoa, man, that's deep.

350
00:23:57,100 --> 00:23:59,568
我们我们已抵达了尽头
I think we've reached the end of the line.

351
00:23:59,700 --> 00:24:02,931
相信我所说的话吧
You took the words right out of my mouth.

352
00:24:03,060 --> 00:24:04,812
山姆,拔剑!
Sam, your sword!

353
00:24:04,940 --> 00:24:07,090
长官! 冲锋!
Sir! En garde!

354
00:24:10,500 --> 00:24:12,934
喂,老兄,给和平一个机会
Hey, man, give peace a chance.

355
00:24:13,060 --> 00:24:15,449
现在神仙也救不了你们了
Nobody can save you now.

356
00:24:17,540 --> 00:24:19,656
齐比迪! 齐比迪! 齐比迪!
Zebedee! Zededee! Zebedeeeee!

357
00:24:25,580 --> 00:24:27,172
是你!
You!

358
00:24:27,900 --> 00:24:29,891
我们又见面了
So we meet again.

359
00:24:30,020 --> 00:24:31,692
没错
Indeed.

360
00:24:31,820 --> 00:24:34,459
我等了一万年要报仇
I've waited 10,000 year for my revenge.

361
00:24:34,580 --> 00:24:39,495
诚如你所知道的
复仇这道菜,越冷越够味
And, as you know,revenge is a dish best served cold.

362
00:24:40,420 --> 00:24:43,093
有些人喜欢热食,齐贝!
Some like it hot, Zeebad!

363
00:24:55,220 --> 00:24:59,213
我底下还有些弹簧呢,齐贝
I've still got some spring in my step,Zeebad.

364
00:25:07,860 --> 00:25:09,657
漂亮,齐比迪!
Well done, Zebedee!

365
00:25:09,780 --> 00:25:12,658
-哦,不
-我想弹簧已经弹掉了
- Oh, no.- I think the spring has sprung.

366
00:25:15,900 --> 00:25:18,130
喂! 你们想去哪呀?
Oi! Where do you think you lot are going?

367
00:25:20,140 --> 00:25:21,493
山姆?
Sam?

368
00:25:21,620 --> 00:25:24,339
山姆! 住手!
考虑清楚你在干嘛
Sam! Stop!Think about what you're doing.

369
00:25:24,460 --> 00:25:25,813
我的任务不是考虑
It's not my job to think.

370
00:25:25,940 --> 00:25:28,215
我是士兵,就遵守命令呀
I'm a soldier. I'm just following orders.

371
00:25:28,340 --> 00:25:32,413
你或许穿着军服,山姆但心里面想的才重要
You may wear a soldier's uniform,Sam, but it's what's inside that counts.

372
00:25:32,540 --> 00:25:33,529
小心!
Look out!

373
00:25:35,500 --> 00:25:36,853
哎呀
Blimey.

374
00:25:36,980 --> 00:25:39,050
逃! 快逃!
Run! Run!

375
00:25:39,180 --> 00:25:41,171
大伙快点,我们的机会来了
Come on, gang, here's our chance.

376
00:25:46,100 --> 00:25:48,773
小胡子让开!喔,差点变牙签了
Move that moustache!Oops, nearly a toothpick.

377
00:26:06,740 --> 00:26:13,009
你在阳光下的日子结束了齐比迪,你这心软的弹簧!
Your days in the sun are over,Zebedee, you benevolent bed spring!

378
00:26:13,140 --> 00:26:16,416
现在该轮到齐贝的时代了!
Now it's time for Zeebad!

379
00:26:19,660 --> 00:26:21,491
停! 齐比迪有麻烦了!
Stop! Zebedee's in trouble!

380
00:26:21,620 --> 00:26:23,417
不,救你们自己吧!
No, save yourselves!

381
00:26:23,540 --> 00:26:25,292
怎么办? 怎么办?
What shall we do? What shall we do?

382
00:26:25,420 --> 00:26:28,139
我们不能丢下他不官救他!
Well, we can't leave him.To the rescue!

383
00:26:30,340 --> 00:26:32,934
你们得去找钻石!
You've got to find the diamonds!

384
00:26:44,220 --> 00:26:47,417
结束了
Ah, so it ends.

385
00:26:47,540 --> 00:26:50,896
我的仇人终于永远消失了
My nemesis finally vanquished forever.

386
00:26:51,020 --> 00:26:54,899
去取得钻石!
Get the diamonds!

387
00:26:55,940 --> 00:26:58,500
不!
Noooooo!

388
00:26:59,700 --> 00:27:01,975
没得选择了,现在一定要离开
We have no choice.We must leave now.

389
00:27:02,100 --> 00:27:03,977
这里我们再也帮不上忙了
There's nothing more we can do here.

390
00:27:08,340 --> 00:27:10,251
-快点,嘟狗-快
- Come on, Doog.- Quick.

391
00:27:11,340 --> 00:27:13,808
掉一滴泪差不多就够了
It's almost enough to make one weep,

392
00:27:13,940 --> 00:27:18,013
若非我这么非常非常快乐的话哈哈!
if only I wasn't so very, very happy.Ha, ha!

393
00:27:18,140 --> 00:27:21,928
现在什么也阻挡不了我了!
Now nothing can stand in my way!

394
00:27:31,380 --> 00:27:35,055
不对,山姆
要从喉咙后面发出来
No, Sam.It's all in the back of the throat.

395
00:27:47,540 --> 00:27:50,532
此时就算我能说话也不晓得该说什么了
Right now, even if I could speak,I wouldn't know what to say.

396
00:27:51,300 --> 00:27:54,098
不敢相信他竟然真的走了
I can't believe he's really gone.

397
00:27:54,220 --> 00:27:58,133
齐比死了,宝贝,齐比死了
Zeb's dead, baby. Zeb's dead.

398
00:27:58,260 --> 00:28:01,616
现在谁来救佛罗伦丝和孩子们呢?
And now who's going to help Florence and the children?

399
00:28:01,820 --> 00:28:03,219
谁会帮助我们?
Who's going to help us?

400
00:28:03,340 --> 00:28:05,296
坚强点,爱蜜楚
Be strong, Ermintrude.

401
00:28:05,420 --> 00:28:07,934
我们必须勇敢起来找到钻石
We have to be brave and find the diamonds.

402
00:28:08,060 --> 00:28:12,451
毕竟那是齐比迪的临终愿望
After all,
that was Zebedee's dying wish.

403
00:28:22,100 --> 00:28:23,818
情形不妙,老兄
It's no good, man.

404
00:28:23,940 --> 00:28:26,215
少了齐比迪,我们一无是处
Without Zebedee, we're nothing.

405
00:28:30,860 --> 00:28:32,691
不,布莱恩说的对
No, Brian's right.

406
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:34,651
我们要拯救我们的世界
We're gonna save our world.

407
00:28:34,780 --> 00:28:36,498
地图在哪?
Now where's the map?

408
00:28:38,500 --> 00:28:41,219
那边! 朝向那边最高峰
There! Head for the tallest mountain
in that range.

409
00:28:41,340 --> 00:28:43,171
就是那股精神,布莱恩!
That's the spirit, Brian!

410
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:47,373
现在上刀山下油锅也阻止不了我取得钻石的决心
Nothing short of a sea of boiling lava will keep me from that diamond now.

411
00:28:48,020 --> 00:28:50,011
哦,蜜糖
Oh, sugar.

412
00:28:50,580 --> 00:28:52,810
钻石就在那里
Well, that's where the diamond is.

413
00:28:52,940 --> 00:28:54,771
谁去拿?
Who's going to get it?

414
00:28:54,900 --> 00:28:58,529
钻石是女孩最好的朋友快过去吧,爱蜜楚
Ah, well, diamonds are a girl's best friend. Off you trot, Ermintrude.

415
00:28:58,660 --> 00:29:01,538
钻石应该由男士交给淑女而不是反过来才对
Men are supposed to give ladies diamonds. Not the other way round.

416
00:29:01,660 --> 00:29:03,776
嘿,我以为狗狗才该去接取的
Hey, I thought dogs
were supposed to fetch.

417
00:29:03,900 --> 00:29:08,257
我的优点一向是“坐下,嘟狗”以及“待着,嘟狗,待着”
My forte's always been "sit, Dougal".That, and "Stay, Dougal, stay".

418
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:12,089
狄伦...你这么勇敢的兔子一定只要稍微跳一下就过去了
Dylan...surely it's only a short hop for such a brave bunny.

419
00:29:12,220 --> 00:29:14,256
对个呆兔子来说比较像是一落千丈
More like a long drop for a dumb rabbit.

420
00:29:14,380 --> 00:29:15,938
安静!
Quiet!

421
00:29:16,460 --> 00:29:18,291
那边有座桥
Ahem. There's a bridge over there.

422
00:29:18,420 --> 00:29:22,777
我想我应该在这里警戒你们过桥到另一边...
I think I ought to keep a lookout here
while you lot cross to the other s...

423
00:29:22,900 --> 00:29:25,573
他不是狗,是胆小鬼
He's not a dog, he's a chicken.

424
00:29:25,700 --> 00:29:27,656
好吧好吧,我懂
All right, all right. I understand.

425
00:29:27,780 --> 00:29:29,611
没我带队你们不肯去
You don't want to go
without your leader.

426
00:29:29,740 --> 00:29:31,219
少往自己脸上贴金了
Talk about wag your own tail.

427
00:29:31,340 --> 00:29:33,171
哦,我惧高
Oooh, I'm scared of heights.

428
00:29:33,300 --> 00:29:36,417
别担忧高度...你要担忧的是宽度才对
Don't worry about them -it's the widths you have to worry about.

429
00:29:36,540 --> 00:29:38,212
这事轻而易举
This is gonna be easy.

430
00:29:38,340 --> 00:29:40,092
-小心点!-很容易嘛
- Careful!- Easy does it.

431
00:29:40,220 --> 00:29:43,656
-离边边只差一点点-别往下看就是
- A bit close to the edge.- Just don't look down.

432
00:29:46,020 --> 00:29:47,976
笔直看着前方
Look straight ahead.

433
00:29:51,500 --> 00:29:53,809
哦,滚烫的岩浆,老天!
Ooh, hot rocks, man!

434
00:29:53,940 --> 00:29:55,612
眼睛看着路面!
Keep your eyes on the road!

435
00:29:55,740 --> 00:29:58,618
-什...什么路面?-没问题的,别担心
- Wha... What road, man?- I'm on it. Don't worry.

436
00:29:58,740 --> 00:30:00,492
干嘛停下来?
Why have you stopped?

437
00:30:00,620 --> 00:30:02,770
一次一步
One step at a time.

438
00:30:02,900 --> 00:30:04,777
哦,没错,哦...
Oh, yeah, oh...

439
00:30:07,380 --> 00:30:10,053
前进了,这会很容易的
There we go. This is gonna be easy.

440
00:30:13,380 --> 00:30:15,018
不!
Noooo!

441
00:30:19,540 --> 00:30:21,212
狄伦! 想想办法!
Dylan! Do something!

442
00:30:21,340 --> 00:30:23,410
你们就不能一个跳出去推吗?
Can't one of you
just hop out and push?

443
00:30:23,540 --> 00:30:26,338
我完全没受过火车训练
Whoa. I'm totally not train trained.

444
00:30:26,460 --> 00:30:28,451
那样说根本没帮助,狄伦!
That's not helping, Dylan!

445
00:30:33,860 --> 00:30:37,819
加上一段铁轨和一罐热油
Ah, for a nice siding
and a can of warm oil.

446
00:30:39,660 --> 00:30:41,298
无须惊慌
No need to panic.

447
00:30:41,420 --> 00:30:43,331
现在才该惊慌
Now. Now is a good time to panic.

448
00:30:50,580 --> 00:30:52,810
摇滚,老天!
Rock and roll, man!

449
00:30:52,940 --> 00:30:54,168
棒极了
Brilliant.

450
00:30:54,300 --> 00:30:56,291
我受够了大众传输工具!
I've had it with public transport!

451
00:31:03,820 --> 00:31:05,538
钻石!
The diamond!

452
00:31:06,780 --> 00:31:08,418
就在那里!
And there you have it!

453
00:31:08,540 --> 00:31:11,452
我已带领各位找到了第一颗钻石!
- I have led you all to the first diamond!
- Wow!

454
00:31:11,580 --> 00:31:14,048
狄伦,头彩就让给你,好吗?
Dylan, do the honours, would you?

455
00:31:15,980 --> 00:31:18,096
嗯,酷
Yeah. Cool.

456
00:31:18,220 --> 00:31:21,178
我想这东西需要调整
Er, I-I think this thing needs tuning.

457
00:31:22,220 --> 00:31:23,573
有事要发生了!
Something's happening!

458
00:31:28,380 --> 00:31:31,497
-我的脚冻僵了-我好冷
- My feet are frozen.- I'm cold.

459
00:31:31,620 --> 00:31:34,009
加油,孩子们我们...我们必须勇敢才行
Come on, children.We... We have to be brave.

460
00:31:34,140 --> 00:31:36,370
看! 是佛罗伦丝!
Look! It's Florence!

461
00:31:37,940 --> 00:31:40,738
奇怪,刚才我以为听到了...
Strange. For a second there,
I thought I heard...

462
00:31:41,700 --> 00:31:43,930
哦...我一定是快疯了
Oh... I must be going mad.

463
00:31:44,060 --> 00:31:46,016
她能听见我! 佛罗伦丝!
She can hear me! Florence!

464
00:31:46,140 --> 00:31:48,290
是我嘟狗呀,我来救你了!
It's me, Dougal. I've come to save you!

465
00:31:48,420 --> 00:31:50,331
嘟狗? 是你吗?
Dougal? Is that you?

466
00:31:51,340 --> 00:31:53,217
-怎么? 不!
-嘟狗?
- What? No!- Dougal?

467
00:31:53,340 --> 00:31:54,693
-她逐渐消失了!
-嘟狗!
- She's fading!- Dougal!

468
00:31:54,820 --> 00:31:58,733
才一天光景
且孩子们迅速结冻中
It's only been one day and the children are freezing fast.

469
00:32:01,340 --> 00:32:04,855
担忧你们的朋友吗?
哈哈哈!
Concerned for your friends?Ha, ha, ha!

470
00:32:07,100 --> 00:32:10,137
我也要拿走地图,请
And I'll take the map too, please.

471
00:32:10,260 --> 00:32:12,774
等等,你怎会知道有...
Wait, how do you know there's a...

472
00:32:18,380 --> 00:32:20,530
他们逼供成招的!
Well, they tortured it out of me!

473
00:32:21,540 --> 00:32:23,974
地图给我!
Give me that map!

474
00:32:27,740 --> 00:32:30,208
-请!
-等我死掉再说!
- Please!- Over my dead body!

475
00:32:30,340 --> 00:32:33,013
山姆,拿出大蒜奶油来!
Sam, get out the garlic butter!

476
00:32:33,140 --> 00:32:35,574
我觉得有点儿嘴馋
I'm feeling a little peckish.

477
00:32:35,700 --> 00:32:37,019
你吹牛
You're bluffing.

478
00:32:37,140 --> 00:32:40,291
试试看呀,你这无骨的粘液!
Try me, you spineless slime-spreader!

479
00:32:40,420 --> 00:32:41,569
少惹他!
Leave him alone!

480
00:32:42,820 --> 00:32:44,617
地图拿去吧
Take the map.

481
00:32:44,740 --> 00:32:47,095
你真是卑鄙的恶魔!
You're a despicable fiend!

482
00:32:47,220 --> 00:32:49,450
我知道,哈哈哈
那是天生的,真的
I know, ha, ha, ha. It's a gift, really.

483
00:32:49,580 --> 00:32:52,140
同情是天大的弱点
Compassion is such a weakness.

484
00:32:52,260 --> 00:32:54,410
抱歉我们无法留下来
不过你们知道情形的
Sorry we can't stay but you know how it is.

485
00:32:54,620 --> 00:32:58,090
一统万民,冰冻天下
- People to rule, places to freeze.- Hup, hup, hup!

486
00:32:58,220 --> 00:33:00,780
快点,智障
我们得毁掉这座桥!
Come on, imbecile,we have to destroy the bridge!

487
00:33:02,860 --> 00:33:05,533
再见了,废物们!
So long, suckers!

488
00:33:21,860 --> 00:33:23,612
等一下
Hold up.

489
00:33:33,140 --> 00:33:34,858
干的好,士兵!
Good work, soldier!

490
00:33:34,980 --> 00:33:37,016
孺子可教也
There's hope for you yet.

491
00:33:37,140 --> 00:33:38,937
谢谢你,长官!
Thank you, sir!

492
00:33:39,060 --> 00:33:40,334
好险!
Cor!

493
00:33:40,460 --> 00:33:45,056
老天,他们不像以前那样
铺设碎石子步道
Man, they don't make crumbling rock causeways like they used to.

494
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:48,536
还有机会...像是长回来吗?
Is there any chance it will, like, grow back?

495
00:33:51,820 --> 00:33:53,731
至少我们平安且暖和
At least we'll be nice and warm.

496
00:33:53,860 --> 00:33:56,818
悲剧啊! 我们死定了!
Oh, tragedy! We're doomed!

497
00:33:57,020 --> 00:33:59,011
我才正要大大扬名呢
And just as I was about to make it big.

498
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:01,813
-你是很大呀
-谢了,嘟狗
- You are big.- Thank you, Dougal.

499
00:34:01,940 --> 00:34:05,569
但我希望我的事业高峰
不会到这火山峰为止
But I was hoping the peak of a volcano wouldn't be the pinnacle of my career.

500
00:34:05,700 --> 00:34:09,488
大伙冷静点
我藏了样东西可能有帮助
Chill out, guys. I've got something stashed that just might help.

501
00:34:09,620 --> 00:34:12,817
狄伦,我们没空用娱乐活动来实验
Dylan, we don't have time to experiment with recreational activities.

502
00:34:12,940 --> 00:34:17,172
齐比迪的魔法盒!
Zebedee's Magic Box!

503
00:34:17,300 --> 00:34:18,813
当然!
Of course!

504
00:34:18,940 --> 00:34:23,138
现在,只要我能弄懂
怎样操作这个东西
Now, if I could just get my head round how to work this thing.

505
00:34:23,260 --> 00:34:25,216
齐比迪有给谁说明书吗?
Did Zebedee give anyone the instructions?

506
00:34:25,340 --> 00:34:27,331
按下按钮就是!
Just press the button!

507
00:34:30,740 --> 00:34:32,492
一艘船,好极了
A boat. Brilliant.

508
00:34:32,620 --> 00:34:34,656
从这儿上船将会一帆风顺
It'll be plain sailing from here on in.

509
00:34:34,780 --> 00:34:37,613
等一下! 我想到了
Wait! I've got it.

510
00:34:37,740 --> 00:34:39,617
搭帐篷!
The tents!

511
00:34:39,740 --> 00:34:41,617
他这回真的疯了
