00:45:18,540 --> 00:45:20,417
我的天鹅湖乃众人津津乐道...
My Swan Lake was the talk of...

688
00:45:20,540 --> 00:45:24,249
少说些有的没的,快救我们出去!
Stop milking the moment and get me out of here!

689
00:45:48,460 --> 00:45:51,213
漂亮! 真是超...
Well done! That was bril...

690
00:45:59,340 --> 00:46:01,092
不!
No-oooo!

691
00:46:29,820 --> 00:46:33,779
我想没人懂得武功吧?
I don't suppose anyone knows anything about martial arts?

692
00:46:34,620 --> 00:46:40,058
只是一些基本的,像是功夫
空手道、柔道、剑道、跆拳道
Just the basics of, like, kung fu, karate,judo, kendo, tae kwon do,

693
00:46:40,180 --> 00:46:42,819
样样都会道,以及...太极拳
anything-you-can-do and...t'ai chi.

694
00:46:42,940 --> 00:46:45,090
有附蛋炒饭吗?
Oooh!Do they come with egg fried rice?

695
00:46:45,220 --> 00:46:47,734
狄伦...你能打倒他们吗?
Dylan...can you beat them up?

696
00:46:47,860 --> 00:46:50,294
对不起,我不崇尚暴力
Sorry, I don't believe in violence.

697
00:46:54,900 --> 00:46:56,731
自卫例外
Except in self-defence.

698
00:47:04,580 --> 00:47:09,335
老天! 那才叫我所谓的振作起来
Oh, man! That's what I call pulling yourself together.

699
00:47:12,860 --> 00:47:14,009
呀! 呀!
Ya! Ya!

700
00:47:17,860 --> 00:47:20,932
-放马过来吧,老兄
-狄伦!
- Wa! Ta! Come on, man.- Dylan!

701
00:47:26,620 --> 00:47:28,850
我不光有漂亮脸蛋而已!
I'm not just another pretty face!

702
00:47:38,340 --> 00:47:42,128
精彩的团队合作
马上取走钻石离开吧
Good group effort. Now, let's grab the diamond and head off.

703
00:47:45,500 --> 00:47:47,297
我是火车,我有汽笛
I'm a train, I have a whistle.

704
00:47:49,380 --> 00:47:53,214
这底下好暗
幸好我有隧道照明,嘻嘻!
It's dark down here.Lucky I have tunnel vision, hee, hee!

705
00:47:57,140 --> 00:47:59,734
超大引擎、合金轮子...
Big engine, alloy wheels...

706
00:48:01,060 --> 00:48:03,699
我可绝对不想落到那付下场
You wouldn't want to be on the wrong end of that.

707
00:48:17,100 --> 00:48:18,772
所以...
So...

708
00:48:18,900 --> 00:48:25,169
传说中的英勇战士
已经来取钻石了!
The fearless warrior of legendhas come to claim the diamond!

709
00:48:25,300 --> 00:48:29,339
不完全是
英勇战士今天没办法来
Erm, no actually, the fearless warrior couldn't make it today,

710
00:48:29,460 --> 00:48:30,939
所以换我们代替
so we came instead.

711
00:48:31,060 --> 00:48:33,290
我们回家途中会交给他的
Er, we'll drop it in to him on the way home.

712
00:48:33,420 --> 00:48:37,652
听着,你到底要不要钻石?
Look, do you want the diamond or don't you?

713
00:48:37,780 --> 00:48:40,578
如果你是在提议的话...是的,请!
Er, well, if you're offering...yes, please!

714
00:48:40,700 --> 00:48:42,452
我想到个更好的主意
I've got a better idea.

715
00:48:42,580 --> 00:48:44,298
我们扑上去吧!
Let's jump him!

716
00:48:44,420 --> 00:48:48,015
冲啊...
Chaaaaaa...

717
00:48:58,740 --> 00:49:00,219
只是想想而已啦
It was just a thought.

718
00:49:00,340 --> 00:49:02,729
要不然就...溜之大吉!
How about...run away!

719
00:49:05,020 --> 00:49:06,373
糟糕!
Oh, no!

720
00:49:13,700 --> 00:49:14,735
救命呀!
He-He-Help!

721
00:49:14,860 --> 00:49:16,373
救命!
Help!

722
00:49:16,500 --> 00:49:19,537
应该是狗啃骨头
不是骨头啃狗!
Dogs are meant to eat bones,not the other way around!

723
00:49:36,860 --> 00:49:38,930
脑筋转的真快,嘟狗
That was quick thinking, Dougal.

724
00:49:39,060 --> 00:49:40,891
是啊,只要你保持镇静
Yeah, well, if you keep your cool

725
00:49:41,020 --> 00:49:44,012
别像只无头苍蝇到处晃...
没时间聊天了
and don't run around like a headless chicken... No time for chitchat.

726
00:49:44,140 --> 00:49:46,938
我们拿了钻石就离开吧
Let's grab that diamond and get out.

727
00:49:48,340 --> 00:49:49,455
不见了!
It's gone!

728
00:49:51,380 --> 00:49:54,258
一群傻瓜! 在找这个吗?
Fools! Looking for this?

729
00:49:55,260 --> 00:49:58,058
你最近就是站不稳
You just can't get the staff these days.

730
00:49:58,900 --> 00:50:03,690
现在,要告诉我第三颗钻石在哪吗?
Now, do you want to tell me where the third diamond is?

731
00:50:03,820 --> 00:50:05,094
甭想
Nope.

732
00:50:05,220 --> 00:50:07,450
反抗无益!
Resistance is futile!

733
00:50:07,580 --> 00:50:10,299
你们不是伟大齐贝的对手!
You're no match for the great Zeebad!

734
00:50:10,420 --> 00:50:11,739
骄者必败
Pride comes before a fall.

735
00:50:11,860 --> 00:50:13,373
嘟狗! 现在!
Dougal! Now!

736
00:50:15,260 --> 00:50:17,330
万岁!
那是见最后一面了
Hooray!That's the last we'll see of them.

737
00:50:25,660 --> 00:50:27,218
他会丢脸丢死了!
That took him down a peg or ten!

738
00:50:27,340 --> 00:50:30,855
对,只不过你刚刚冲掉了
一号钻石和二号钻石
Yeah, man, except you just flushedaway diamonds one and two.

739
00:50:30,980 --> 00:50:33,289
那...我们现在要去哪?
So...where do we go now?

740
00:50:33,420 --> 00:50:36,298
我们得尽快赶回旋转木马那里
We must get back to the Roundaboutas fast as we can.

741
00:50:36,420 --> 00:50:38,615
我知道好比“祸害遗千年”
I know there's like,"no rest for the wicked",

742
00:50:38,740 --> 00:50:42,289
不过我是好人
此刻我需要睡个午觉
but I'm one of the good guys and right now I need a siesta.

743
00:50:46,500 --> 00:50:47,853
看!
Look!

744
00:50:47,980 --> 00:50:49,857
声音! 我就知道他们会来救我
Voices! I knew they'd come to rescue me.

745
00:50:49,980 --> 00:50:52,858
等等,也许应该由我去救他们
Hang on, maybe I'm supposed to be rescuing them.

746
00:50:55,900 --> 00:50:58,858
嘿,听起来好熟悉
Hey, that sound's familiar.

747
00:50:58,980 --> 00:51:02,097
典型的火车声
总是在绝望时出现
Typical train. Always turns up when you least expect it.

748
00:51:02,220 --> 00:51:04,734
各位快点,走了
Come on, gang. In we go.

749
00:51:04,940 --> 00:51:06,453
哦,不
Oh, no.

750
00:51:08,300 --> 00:51:10,211
好,我们离开这儿吧
Right, now, let's get out of here.

751
00:51:10,340 --> 00:51:12,900
开慢点,你令我的乳汁翻搅
Oh, do slow down,you're making my milk churn.

752
00:51:13,020 --> 00:51:15,488
你在说笑吗?
我们慢得跟蜗牛似的!
Are you kidding?We're moving at a snail's pace!

753
00:51:15,620 --> 00:51:17,053
慢得跟蜗牛刚好适合我
Snail's pace suits me just fine.

754
00:51:17,180 --> 00:51:19,535
哦,爱蜜楚!
Oh, Ermintrude!

755
00:51:19,660 --> 00:51:21,651
那是你说过最窝心的话
That's the sweetest thing you've ever said.

756
00:51:21,780 --> 00:51:23,452
放松点,嘟狗
Relax, Doogie.

757
00:51:23,580 --> 00:51:26,253
不久这整个疯狂之旅
将会抛到我们脑后
Soon this whole crazy trip will be behind us.

758
00:51:26,380 --> 00:51:28,098
在我们后面!
Behind us!

759
00:51:28,220 --> 00:51:31,132
-我就是这意思
-不! 在我们后面!
- That's what I said, man.- No! Behind us!

760
00:51:33,140 --> 00:51:34,858
快一点! 再快一点!
Faster! Faster!

761
00:51:36,940 --> 00:51:37,929
低头!
Duck!

762
00:51:42,460 --> 00:51:44,416
我一直想当云霄飞车!
I always wanted to be a roller coaster!

763
00:51:46,300 --> 00:51:47,574
哇,兄弟!
Whoa, dudes!

764
00:51:47,700 --> 00:51:49,418
谈谈差点进鬼门关的经验吧
Talk about a near-death experience.

765
00:51:49,540 --> 00:51:51,610
我想我看到隧道尽头有光芒
I thought I saw the light at the end of the tunnel.

766
00:51:51,740 --> 00:51:54,413
这正是隧道尽头的光芒!
That is the light at the end of the tunnel!

767
00:51:54,540 --> 00:51:56,212
我们就快脱险了!
We're going to be OK!

768
00:51:56,340 --> 00:51:58,729
而齐贝依然困在神殿里!
And Zeebad's still trapped in the temple!

769
00:52:01,940 --> 00:52:06,013
那么那是谁?
他的邪恶双胞胎齐贝德吗?
Then, like, who's that,his evil twin, Zeebadder?

770
00:52:10,940 --> 00:52:13,613
我的第三颗钻石在哪里?
Where's my third diamond?

771
00:52:18,660 --> 00:52:22,892
锅炉,现在别输掉!
Whoa! Furnace, don't fail me now!

772
00:52:32,860 --> 00:52:35,090
大家抓稳了!
Brace yourself, everybody!

773
00:52:35,220 --> 00:52:37,336
注意断轨!
Whoa! Mind the gap!

774
00:52:41,220 --> 00:52:42,209
嘿!
Hey!

775
00:52:46,980 --> 00:52:48,936
大鼻子来也!
Here comes big nose!

776
00:52:55,020 --> 00:52:56,533
谁快想想办法!
Somebody do something!

777
00:52:57,060 --> 00:53:01,212
嘿,这一定是某种反跳跃装置
Hey, this must be some kinda anti-spring device.

778
00:53:01,340 --> 00:53:03,535
-这会教齐贝慢下来
-真的?
- This'll slow Zeebad down.- Really?

779
00:53:03,660 --> 00:53:06,333
也可能是弹跳座椅
- Aaaagh!- Or it could be an ejector seat.

780
00:53:09,540 --> 00:53:11,929
那究竟是啥声音?
What the devil was that?

781
00:53:12,060 --> 00:53:14,096
发生什么事? 我为何瞎了?
What happened? Why am I blind?

782
00:53:14,220 --> 00:53:16,017
我们到达旋转木马了吗?
Did we reach the Roundabout yet?

783
00:53:17,020 --> 00:53:19,693
原来我们要往那里!
So that's where you're headed!

784
00:53:19,820 --> 00:53:20,935
旋转木马!
The Roundabout!

785
00:53:21,060 --> 00:53:24,689
在那里就可找到我的钻石了!
And that's where I'll find my diamond!

786
00:53:24,820 --> 00:53:27,539
再见了,粘球!
So long, slimeball!

787
00:53:31,060 --> 00:53:34,177
山姆,上去车顶除掉囚犯
Sam, get up on the roof and dispose of the prisoner.

788
00:53:34,300 --> 00:53:35,813
除掉囚犯?
Dispose of a prisoner?

789
00:53:35,940 --> 00:53:38,090
不能那么做,长官
那样违反日内瓦公约
Can't do that, sir. Geneva Convention.

790
00:53:38,220 --> 00:53:40,609
你猜怎样? 我管它公不公约!
Guess what? I'm unconventional!

791
00:53:43,620 --> 00:53:45,656
管它公不公约,哈哈哈!
Un-con-ventional. Ha, ha, ha!

792
00:53:45,780 --> 00:53:47,372
斩断他的头!
Off with his head!

793
00:53:47,500 --> 00:53:49,616
啊! 救命呀!
Aaaargh! He-eeelp!

794
00:53:49,740 --> 00:53:51,219
布莱恩!
Brian!

795
00:53:59,820 --> 00:54:04,132
-欢迎上车!
-爱蜜楚,你救了我!
- Welcome aboard!- Ermintrude, you saved me!

796
00:54:06,940 --> 00:54:09,534
别想穿越我
你这花枝招展的开罐器!
Don't cross me,you tarted-up tin opener!

797
00:54:09,660 --> 00:54:11,776
快一点,你这百合肝叛徒!
Faster, you lily-livered traitor!

798
00:54:11,900 --> 00:54:13,538
我要抢到那颗钻石!
I want that diamond!

799
00:54:13,660 --> 00:54:15,332
多加点煤炭!
More coal!

800
00:54:21,180 --> 00:54:22,693
哦! 不!
Oh! No!

801
00:54:22,820 --> 00:54:24,731
前面轨道合并!
Trouble dead ahead!

802
00:54:25,740 --> 00:54:27,139
那是我的轨道!
That's my line!

803
00:54:30,540 --> 00:54:34,897
这就是你们不让路的结果!
Now, this is what happens when you don't brush regularly!

804
00:54:40,740 --> 00:54:43,129
长官! 压力...过高!
Sir! The pressure - it's too much!

805
00:54:43,260 --> 00:54:45,057
我知道,我知道!
I know, I know!

806
00:54:45,180 --> 00:54:49,173
有时候我觉得
我要大发神经了!
Sometimes I feel I'm going quite insane!

807
00:54:49,300 --> 00:54:50,972
不,长官,是锅炉!
No, sir, it's the boiler!

808
00:54:51,100 --> 00:54:52,089
是...
It's...

809
00:54:54,860 --> 00:54:58,409
谢天谢地! 我们安全了!
Thank goodness! We're safe!

810
00:54:58,540 --> 00:55:00,371
我称那爆炸为蒸汽烟火!
I call that letting off steam!

811
00:55:00,500 --> 00:55:01,649
哇!
- Hurrah!- Whoa!

812
00:55:03,060 --> 00:55:05,654
我能飞了!
I can fly-y-y!

813
00:55:06,900 --> 00:55:07,889
不,我不能
No, I can't.

814
00:55:14,020 --> 00:55:16,932
今天一天已经飞够了!
Oh, that's enough flying for one day!

815
00:55:17,060 --> 00:55:19,972
我们得比齐贝早一步
赶到旋转木马
We've got to get to the Round about before Zeebad.

816
00:55:20,740 --> 00:55:24,369
等等,齐贝并不知道
钻石在旋转木马那儿
Hang on, Zeebad doesn't know the diamond's at the Roundabout.

817
00:55:24,500 --> 00:55:26,889
严格说来并不正确...
Erm... Well, that's not strictly true...

818
00:55:27,020 --> 00:55:28,533
那时候,在火车上...
Back there, on the Train...

819
00:55:28,660 --> 00:55:31,891
我一时糊涂就...
就脱口而出了
I-I was confused and it...it just slipped out.

820
00:55:32,020 --> 00:55:33,169
布莱恩,老兄!
Brian, man!

821
00:55:33,300 --> 00:55:35,530
话已覆水难收
Well there's no use crying over spilt milk.

822
00:55:35,660 --> 00:55:37,537
你说的倒轻松
That's easy for you to say.

823
00:55:37,660 --> 00:55:39,457
大家快点,上火车!
Come on, people. To the Train!

824
00:55:44,220 --> 00:55:47,337
看样子火车已经停驶了
Whoa. Looks like this service has been cancelled.

825
00:55:47,460 --> 00:55:48,893
-你不要紧吧?
-嗯
- Are you all right?- Yeah.

826
00:55:49,020 --> 00:55:50,578
可能要误点了
Delays look likely.

827
00:55:50,700 --> 00:55:52,452
我想我已拉了活塞
I think I've pulled a piston.

828
00:55:52,580 --> 00:55:54,935
不,不会这样子的
Ow! Nope, it's not gonna happen.

829
00:55:55,060 --> 00:55:56,778
可怜的小火车!
Oh, poor Trainy!

830
00:55:56,900 --> 00:55:59,095
太阳快下山了
Oh, the sun's setting.

831
00:55:59,220 --> 00:56:01,939
只好靠我们自己力量去办了
We'll just have to make it under our own steam.

832
00:56:02,060 --> 00:56:04,415
暂别了,老弟
Goodbye for now, old buddy.

833
00:56:05,580 --> 00:56:07,298
你能办到的
You can make it.

834
00:56:07,420 --> 00:56:08,819
跟着我们的足迹走
Just follow our tracks.

835
00:56:08,940 --> 00:56:12,250
别担心我
你们走吧,去找出钻石
Don't worry about me.You go on, find the diamond.

836
00:56:15,060 --> 00:56:17,858
再想一想... 我怎么办?
On second thoughts... What about me?

837
00:56:21,660 --> 00:56:23,457
烂机器!
Wretched machines!

838
00:56:23,580 --> 00:56:26,378
我一定要赶到旋转木马,趁...
I must reach the Roundabout before...

839
00:56:26,500 --> 00:56:27,933
长官!
Ooh, sir!

840
00:56:28,060 --> 00:56:29,618
我需要医疗
Medic needed.

841
00:56:29,740 --> 00:56:32,618
SOS,求救...
SOS. Mayday. Oooh...

842
00:56:32,740 --> 00:56:34,458
我? 救你?
Me? Help you?

843
00:56:34,580 --> 00:56:38,812
你这软弱无能的迪斯可娃娃!
You treacherou mollusc-sparing disco dolly!

844
00:56:38,940 --> 00:56:41,295
你的职责到此结束
Your tour of duty is over.

845
00:56:41,420 --> 00:56:43,809
你不能遗弃伤兵,长官
You can't leave an injured soldier, sir.

846
00:56:43,940 --> 00:56:45,134
不能吗?
Can't I?

847
00:56:45,260 --> 00:56:47,171
那就等着瞧吧
Just watch me.

848
00:56:48,020 --> 00:56:49,533
等一下!
Wait!

849
00:56:49,660 --> 00:56:51,616
回来!
Come back!

850
00:56:54,020 --> 00:56:57,251
邪恶坏蛋...真够狠心的
Evil villains...can be so cruel.

851
00:57:06,820 --> 00:57:08,253
我走不动了
I can't go on.

852
00:57:08,380 --> 00:57:10,530
我们已经走好几个小时了
We've been walking for hours.

853
00:57:10,660 --> 00:57:12,935
好冷...
It's so c-c-cold.

854
00:57:13,060 --> 00:57:15,449
我手脚都没知觉了
I can't feel my limb.

855
00:57:16,340 --> 00:57:18,649
可是佛罗伦丝...还有孩子们
But Florence...and the children.

856
00:57:18,780 --> 00:57:22,011
如果我们不及早赶到
他们会冻成冰棒的
If we don't get there soon,they'll be frozen stiff.

857
00:57:22,140 --> 00:57:24,608
哦,时间无情之手!
Oh, the cruel hands of time!

858
00:57:24,740 --> 00:57:30,292
但要不是...要不是时间
一切会像是,瞬间发生
But if it... if it wasn't for time,everything would, like, happen at once.

859
00:57:30,420 --> 00:57:33,253
等等,那是什么?
Wait. What's that?

860
00:57:35,260 --> 00:57:38,809
脚印! 也许会带我们回村子里去
Footprints! Maybe they'll lead us back to the village.

861
00:57:38,940 --> 00:57:43,809
可是,好像,有哪种古怪生物
会留下这些脚印?
But, like, what kinda freaky creatures would leave prints like these?

862
00:57:43,940 --> 00:57:46,010
他们一定也是累毙了
They must be exhausted too.

863
00:57:46,140 --> 00:57:50,213
其中一个好像用爬的爬过地面
One of them seems to be crawling along the ground.

864
00:57:50,340 --> 00:57:52,854
我比较喜欢称为“滑过”
I prefer the term gliding.

865
00:57:52,980 --> 00:57:55,016
不! 那是我们的脚印!
Oh, no! They're ours!

866
00:57:55,140 --> 00:57:56,619
哦,不!
Oh, no!

867
00:57:56,740 --> 00:57:58,537
不,不!
No, no!

868
00:57:58,660 --> 00:58:04,292
就这样了,该好好睡上一觉了
Well, that's it, man.It's time for the big sleep.

869
00:58:04,420 --> 00:58:06,217
我们尽力了
We did our best.

870
00:58:06,340 --> 00:58:09,537
但我们的尽力还不够好...
But our best wasn't good enough. Oh...

871
00:58:09,660 --> 00:58:11,616
哦,曲终人散
Oh, it's the final curtain.

872
00:58:14,460 --> 00:58:16,849
不,千万不可睡着
No. We mustn't sleep.

873
00:58:16,980 --> 00:58:18,891
太冷了
It's too cold.

874
00:58:19,780 --> 00:58:21,577
太冷了
It's too cold.

875
00:58:21,700 --> 00:58:23,531
我们千万不可...
We mustn't...

876
00:58:23,660 --> 00:58:25,537
佛罗伦丝...
Florence...

877
00:58:47,820 --> 00:58:50,653
嘟狗!
Doooougaaaal!

878
00:58:51,660 --> 00:58:54,732
-嘟狗?
-佛罗伦丝! 你没事!
- Dougal?- Florence! You're OK!

879
00:58:54,860 --> 00:58:56,930
比没事还要好
I'm more than OK.

880
00:58:57,140 --> 00:59:00,018
我甜蜜无比
I'm swee-eeet.

881
00:59:00,740 --> 00:59:02,810
但旋转木马呢?
But what about the Roundabout?

882
00:59:02,940 --> 00:59:05,852
孩子们呢? 冻的缩成一团
The children? Huddled. Freezing.

883
00:59:05,980 --> 00:59:07,333
别担心,嘟狗
Don't worry, Dougal.

884
00:59:07,460 --> 00:59:09,212
你现在跟我在一起...
You're with me now...

885
00:59:09,340 --> 00:59:13,015
在糖果天堂!
in sugar paradise!

886
00:59:13,820 --> 00:59:18,575
你看,糖果要给我的小乖,嘟狗
Look. Sweets for my sweet Dougal.

887
00:59:22,540 --> 00:59:27,933
喜欢吃多少就吃多少!
And you can eat as much as you like!

888
00:59:31,340 --> 00:59:34,730
不,这样不对!我一定是疯了
N-No, this isn't right!I must be going nuts.

889
00:59:34,860 --> 00:59:37,579
我得醒来,拯救佛罗伦丝
I have to wake up. Save Florence.

890
00:59:37,700 --> 00:59:39,338
佛罗伦丝!
Florence!

891
00:59:39,460 --> 00:59:40,575
不!
No!

892
00:59:40,700 --> 00:59:42,531
只是一场梦
It was just a dream.

893
00:59:42,660 --> 00:59:45,857
佛罗伦丝!
Florence!

894
00:59:47,380 --> 00:59:50,133
佛罗伦丝!
Flore-eeeeence!

895
01:00:09,740 --> 01:00:12,334
快醒醒!
Come on. Wake up!

896
01:00:12,460 --> 01:00:14,291
醒醒! 醒醒!
Wake up! Wake up!

897
01:00:14,420 --> 01:00:19,096
不行,我意识陷入高度恍惚状态
No way, man. I'm in a higher state
of unconsciousness.

898
01:00:19,220 --> 01:00:22,735
天越来越亮了 我们却还完全迷失方向
It's getting light and we're still completely lost.

899
01:00:22,860 --> 01:00:24,657
我不太确定我们是这样
I'm not so sure we are.

900
01:00:27,620 --> 01:00:31,408
哇,真是严重的梦游
Whoa, that was some
serious sleepwalking.

901
01:00:32,660 --> 01:00:34,298
看!
Look!

902
01:00:34,420 --> 01:00:35,933
看,看,看!
Look, look, look!

903
01:00:36,060 --> 01:00:38,369
快! 来看一下!看看那个!
Quick! Come and have a look!Look at that!

904
01:00:38,500 --> 01:00:40,331
真的和我想的是一样吗?
Is that really what I think it is?

905
01:00:40,460 --> 01:00:42,337
家?
Home?

906
01:00:49,900 --> 01:00:51,015
诅咒!
Curses!

907
01:00:51,140 --> 01:00:53,654
钻石一定在这里哪个地方!
The diamond
must be here somewhere!

908
01:00:53,780 --> 01:00:55,133
齐贝!
Zeebad!

909
01:00:55,260 --> 01:00:56,579
你!
You!

910
01:00:56,700 --> 01:00:59,498
这旋转木马不够大容不下我们两个!
This roundabout ain't big enough for the both of us!

911
01:00:59,620 --> 01:01:04,933
当我留下某人等死时就是指望对方死掉
When I leave someone for dead,I expect them to die.

912
01:01:05,060 --> 01:01:07,494
你就不能乖乖死掉吗?
Can't you even do that right? Eh?

913
01:01:07,700 --> 01:01:10,737
自从我离开旋转木马后还没做对过半样事
Oh, I haven't done anything right since I left the Roundabout.

914
01:01:10,860 --> 01:01:13,090
现在是我重整旗鼓的时候了
Now it's time for me
to resume my post.

915
01:01:13,220 --> 01:01:15,814
你? 你本来在旋转木马上面?
You? You were on the Roundabout?

916
01:01:15,940 --> 01:01:17,339
对,我是
Yeah, I was.

917
01:01:17,460 --> 01:01:19,132
阻挡住像你这种人
Guarding it from the likes of you.

918
01:01:19,260 --> 01:01:21,091
哈! 瞧你这付模样!
Ha! Look at the state of you!

919
01:01:21,220 --> 01:01:23,290
连颗水煮蛋都守不住了!
You couldn't guard a boiled egg!

920
01:01:23,420 --> 01:01:26,139
我可能已受到损坏
Well, I might have taken a battering,

921
01:01:26,260 --> 01:01:28,091
不过就像齐比迪跟我说的:
but it's like Zebedee told me:

922
01:01:28,220 --> 01:01:30,336
心里想什么才重要!
it's what's inside that counts!

923
01:01:31,140 --> 01:01:34,894
冲呀!
Chaaaaarge!

924
01:01:46,500 --> 01:01:47,979
钻石!
The diamond!

925
01:01:48,100 --> 01:01:52,491
齐比迪,你这狡猾的家伙
Oooh, Zebedee, you cunning swine.

926
01:01:52,620 --> 01:01:57,933
再想一下,我留你自生自灭
差点就抛弃了钻石
And to think, I nearly abandoned it when I left you to die.

927
01:01:58,060 --> 01:02:00,733
真是讽刺!
Ooh, the irony!

928
01:02:00,860 --> 01:02:05,888
现在,该来天寒地冻了!
Now, time for the big chill!

929
01:02:13,020 --> 01:02:15,056
这不可能是我们的村子
This can't be our village.

930
01:02:15,180 --> 01:02:16,738
我一样都不认得了
I don't recognise a thing.

931
01:02:16,860 --> 01:02:19,818
对,好像,也许我们转错弯了,嘟狗
Yeah, like, maybe we took a wrong turn, Doog.

932
01:02:19,940 --> 01:02:22,010
不,不,绝对是这里
No, no, this is definitely it.

933
01:02:22,140 --> 01:02:24,495
只要我们经过这个白色东东
If we go past this white thingy

934
01:02:24,620 --> 01:02:26,417
再经过这个白色的...
and by this white bit...

935
01:02:26,540 --> 01:02:28,849
转角过去应该就是...
just round the corner should be the...

936
01:02:32,180 --> 01:02:33,249
哦,不!
Oh, no!

937
01:02:48,780 --> 01:02:50,850
哈哈哈!
Ha, ha, ha!

938
01:02:58,740 --> 01:02:59,855
齐贝!
Zeebad!

939
01:03:01,180 --> 01:03:03,011
完美极了!
Ah, perfect!

940
01:03:03,140 --> 01:03:06,337
你们刚好赶上最后一幕
You've arrived just in time for the finale.

941
01:03:06,460 --> 01:03:09,133
再见了,阳光!
So long, sunshine!

942
01:03:22,260 --> 01:03:24,057
佛罗伦丝!
Florence!

943
01:03:31,420 --> 01:03:34,651
哦,佛罗伦丝!
Oh, Florence!

944
01:03:34,780 --> 01:03:38,932
不,不,不,不,不!
Oh, no, no, no, no, no!

945
01:03:39,060 --> 01:03:40,732
全是我的错
This is all my fault.

946
01:03:40,860 --> 01:03:44,933
如果我没那么贪吃、愚蠢
If only I hadn't been so greedy and stupid.

947
01:03:45,580 --> 01:03:49,459
那么再会了,狄伦
再见,亲爱的布莱恩
Farewell, then, Dylan.Goodbye, dear Brian.

948
01:03:49,580 --> 01:03:53,095
爱蜜楚,在我们结冻之前
Er...Ermintrude, before we freeze,

949
01:03:53,220 --> 01:03:56,815
有件事我一直想告诉你...
there's something I've been t-trying to t-tell you...

950
01:04:00,660 --> 01:04:07,691
这家伙严重扰乱我的宿命!
This guy is seriously messing with my karma!

951
01:04:11,460 --> 01:04:16,136
吃这个吧
你这弹跳的恶作剧盒玩具!
Eat this,you jumped-up jack-in-the-box! Ya!

952
01:04:17,060 --> 01:04:21,099
你就是不明白你被打败了,对不对?
Ooof! You just don't know when you're beaten, do you?

953
01:04:22,740 --> 01:04:24,890
吃颗寒气丸吧,兔子!
Take a chill pill, rabbit!

954
01:04:31,300 --> 01:04:33,530
等一下,就是那样!
Wait a minute. That's it!

955
01:04:33,660 --> 01:04:36,732
爱蜜楚,唱歌!
能唱多大声就唱多大声!
Ermintrude, sing!Sing as loud as you can!

956
01:04:41,100 --> 01:04:43,853
我不习惯在这种情况下演唱!
I'm not used to working under these conditions!

957
01:04:43,980 --> 01:04:45,811
嘟狗可能想到了什么法子
Dougal might be onto something.

958
01:04:45,940 --> 01:04:48,579
对! 爱蜜楚! 快唱!
Yes! Ermintrude! Sing!

959
01:04:48,700 --> 01:04:50,611
我还没暖嗓呢!
I haven't even warmed up!

960
01:04:50,740 --> 01:04:52,776
爱蜜楚! 快唱!
Ermintrude! Sing!

961
01:04:53,500 --> 01:04:55,058
好啦
Fine.

962
01:04:58,220 --> 01:05:01,929
那是什么讨厌的噪音啊?
What is that abominable noise?

963
01:05:23,660 --> 01:05:25,013
装填弹药!
Shell loaded!

964
01:05:27,180 --> 01:05:28,169
吃这招吧!
Take this!

965
01:05:28,300 --> 01:05:29,653
快逃!
Run!

966
01:05:30,900 --> 01:05:33,812
准备好没? 瞄准,发射!
Ready? Aim. Fire!

967
01:05:38,260 --> 01:05:39,978
漂亮!
Well done!

968
01:05:47,660 --> 01:05:49,378
狄伦,往你那边去了!
Dylan, it's coming your way!

969
01:05:49,500 --> 01:05:53,459
哇,这一撞可不轻!
Whoa, that was some hit!

970
01:05:54,380 --> 01:05:57,690
哇! 棒透了!
Whoa! Psy-che-delic!

971
01:06:05,060 --> 01:06:07,016
我来挥棒
I got it, man.

972
01:06:08,740 --> 01:06:09,729
不!
No!

973
01:06:13,460 --> 01:06:15,132
给我! 给我!
Over to me! Over to me!

974
01:06:15,260 --> 01:06:17,728
不! 是我的! 我的! 哈哈!
No! It's mine! Mine! Ha, ha!

975
01:06:24,060 --> 01:06:25,049
二比零!
Two-nil!

976
01:06:25,180 --> 01:06:27,535
比赛还没结束呢
The game's not over yet.

977
01:06:29,860 --> 01:06:31,737
接的好,齐贝!
Oooh, nice catch, Zeebad!

978
01:06:31,860 --> 01:06:33,498
现在来抢最后的...
Now let's get the final...

979
01:06:33,620 --> 01:06:34,609
钻石!
diamond!

980
01:06:34,740 --> 01:06:36,332
敢碰它你就死定了
Touch it and you're toast.

981
01:06:36,460 --> 01:06:39,338
你吓不倒我!
你只是个蓝色大混蛋
You don't scare me!You're just a big, blue bully.

982
01:06:39,460 --> 01:06:41,212
现在局势已逆转
Now the tables have turned

983
01:06:41,340 --> 01:06:43,649
我们只需要
把最后这颗钻石放回...
and all we need do is put this last diamond back on...

984
01:06:44,900 --> 01:06:48,097
全垒打出击!
Here comes a home run!

985
01:06:48,220 --> 01:06:49,778
休想!
Not again!

986
01:06:59,700 --> 01:07:01,258
胜利!
Victory!

987
01:07:04,980 --> 01:07:08,256
就差这么一点...
So close and yet so...

988
01:07:08,380 --> 01:07:10,177
太好了!
far out!

989
01:07:10,300 --> 01:07:13,372
对一群呆子动物而言
做的还不错!
Nice try - for a bunch of dumb animals!

990
01:07:13,500 --> 01:07:16,412
不过动物园关闭时间到了
But now it's closing time at the zoo.

991
01:07:16,540 --> 01:07:20,738
用我们的秘密武器就不会
齐比迪的魔法盒!
Not with our secret weapon:Zebedee's magic box!

992
01:07:25,180 --> 01:07:29,810
没有用!
- Huh?
- Ya!

993
01:07:39,460 --> 01:07:41,894
现在齐比迪的玩具
也帮不了你们了
It d-doesn't work. Aw!

994
01:07:43,260 --> 01:07:46,332
我回来了! 呀呼!
Bounce back from that, Slinky!Woo-hoo!

995
01:07:46,460 --> 01:07:48,212
火车! 我就知道你办的到!
Train! I knew you'd make it!

996
01:07:48,340 --> 01:07:50,331
-照时刻表行驶
-钻石!
- Bang on schedule.- The diamond!

997
01:07:50,460 --> 01:07:51,859
我去拿
I'll get it.

998
01:07:51,980 --> 01:07:55,097
我害大家淌这趟浑水
我要救大家出来
I got us into this mess and I'll get us out.

999
01:07:57,180 --> 01:07:58,295
去呀,嘟狗
Go on, Dougal.

1000
01:09:02,500 --> 01:09:04,456
不!
No-ooo-ooo!

1001
01:09:45,540 --> 01:09:47,451
哈哈哈!
Mm-mm! Ha, ha, ha!

1002
01:09:54,460 --> 01:09:56,371
成功了! 成功了!
We did it! We did it!

1003
01:09:56,500 --> 01:09:58,855
成功了! 成功了!
We did it! We did it!

1004
01:10:00,260 --> 01:10:01,659
快点!
Come on!

1005
01:10:03,060 --> 01:10:04,573
干的好!
Well done!

1006
01:10:04,700 --> 01:10:07,168
没什么能像歌剧一样能够破冰
There's nothing like opera
for breaking the ice.

1007
01:10:08,540 --> 01:10:13,056
绿茵映眼帘!甜美苍翠的绿草!
I can see grass, man!Sweet, green grass!

1008
01:10:13,180 --> 01:10:15,091
可是佛罗伦丝人呢?
But where's Florence?

1009
01:10:16,980 --> 01:10:18,413
佛罗伦丝?
Florence?

1010
01:10:20,820 --> 01:10:22,048
佛罗伦丝!
Florence!

1011
01:10:22,900 --> 01:10:24,777
佛罗伦丝,能听见我吗?
Florence, can you hear me?

1012
01:10:24,900 --> 01:10:26,652
拜你醒来
Please wake up.

1013
01:10:26,780 --> 01:10:29,248
拜你醒来,别离开我
Please wake up. Don't leave me.

1014
01:10:29,380 --> 01:10:31,530
没有你,这世界就毫无意义了!
This world means nothing without you!

1015
01:10:31,660 --> 01:10:33,571
我很遗憾,老弟
Sorry, old buddy.

1016
01:10:33,780 --> 01:10:35,259
不,不会的...
No, it can't...

1017
01:10:35,380 --> 01:10:36,779
她不会的...
She can't...

1018
01:10:36,900 --> 01:10:38,618
佛罗伦丝!
Florence!

1019
01:10:38,740 --> 01:10:40,696
我可爱的佛罗伦丝!
My lovely Florence!

1020
01:10:51,500 --> 01:10:52,694
她动了!
She moved!

1021
01:10:56,180 --> 01:10:57,374
她还活着!
She's alive!

1022
01:10:57,500 --> 01:11:00,697
哦,佛罗伦丝!
我以为我永远失去你了!
Oh, Florence!I thought I'd lost you forever!

1023
01:11:00,820 --> 01:11:02,811
我也以为我失去你了,嘟狗
And I thought I'd lost you too, Dougal.

1024
01:11:02,940 --> 01:11:05,056
但你救了我的命
But you saved my life.

1025
01:11:05,180 --> 01:11:06,772
还有大家的命
And everyone else's.

1026
01:11:06,900 --> 01:11:08,458
别说了
Oh, stop it.

1027
01:11:08,580 --> 01:11:10,810
任何超级英雄狗都会这么做的
It's what any incredibly heroic dog would do.

1028
01:11:12,740 --> 01:11:14,696
那么你不想要一份...
So you don't want a...

1029
01:11:14,820 --> 01:11:16,333
小小的奖赏吗?
little reward?

1030
01:11:16,460 --> 01:11:18,052
不用,我已经学乖了
Oh, no. I've learnt my lesson.

1031
01:11:18,180 --> 01:11:20,410
我再也不跟棒棒糖扯上关系了
I'm not having anything more to do with lollipops.

1032
01:11:20,540 --> 01:11:21,859
或口香糖
Or gobstoppers.

1033
01:11:21,980 --> 01:11:23,208
或太妃糖
Or toffees.

1034
01:11:25,060 --> 01:11:27,335
等一下,齐比迪到哪去了?
But wait, where's Zebedee?

1035
01:11:31,460 --> 01:11:32,688
齐比迪!
Zebedee!

1036
01:11:32,820 --> 01:11:35,857
好极了,我的朋友们
我一直明白你们能办到!
Bravo, my friends.I always knew you could do it!

1037
01:11:35,980 --> 01:11:37,413
但我们以为你死了!
But we thought you were dead!

1038
01:11:37,540 --> 01:11:39,337
死了? 胡说,嘟狗!
Dead? Nonsense, Dougal!

1039
01:11:39,460 --> 01:11:43,612
人人都知道冬天过后
就是春天!
Everyone knows that after winter it's time for spring!

1040
01:11:50,180 --> 01:11:52,648
大家快点来坐旋转木马吧!
Come on, everyone.To the Roundabout!

1041
01:12:01,820 --> 01:12:03,617
哦,不!
Oh, no!

1042
01:12:03,740 --> 01:12:05,378
为什么不动?
How come it's not moving?

1043
01:12:05,500 --> 01:12:07,536
好像卡住了
It's like stuck, man.

1044
